cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper focuses on salient object detection in images using deep learning techniques, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The authors also mention the use of superpixels, which is a common technique in image segmentation (cs.MM) and the use of convolutional neural networks (CNNs), which is a popular technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE).
